{
  "_id": "H1jBsPMYx5GH8U4g",
  "name": "Binding Ties",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/blue_05.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a standard action, you can touch an ally and remove one condition affecting the ally by transferring it to yourself. This transfer lasts a number of rounds equal to your cleric level, but you can end it as a free action on your turn. At the end of this effect, the condition reverts to the original creature, unless it has ended or is removed by another effect. While this power is in use, the target is immune to the transferred condition. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your Wisdom modifier.</p>\n<p>This power replaces the Calming Touch power of the Community Domain.</p>"
    },
